  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,Object>
    Deprecated. 
    Use RequestAttributes

    @Deprecated
public class RequestProperties
extends ResolvingObjectMap
    Encapsulates request-level properties.

    These are properties specified for a single HTTP request that extends the properties defined on RestMethodProperties and are accessible and modifiable through the following:

    • RestRequest.getProperties()
    • RestRequest.prop(String, Object)
    • RestResponse.getProperties()
    • RestResponse.prop(String, Object)
    • Overview > juneau-rest-server > Configurable Properties
